lead_paragraph: Kraigg Brathwaite and Shane Dowrich struck unbeaten half-centuries to guide West Indies to a first test victory in 14 matches as the Caribbean side beat Pakistan by five wickets on the final morning of the third test in Sharjah on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: West Indies Beat Pakistan to End Winless Streak
headline.main: West Indies Beat Pakistan to End Winless Streak
